{"title":"张锁买牛","authors":["王亚平"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":3,"day":4}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁买牛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王亚平"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放战争第三年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利消息到处传，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全国胜利已不远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后方加紧闹生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开腔要唱冀鲁豫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一块大平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五谷杂粮收成好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条黄河流中间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄河南北村庄多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民受苦几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的政策好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导穷人把身翻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个村庄颜家店，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个村庄靠河边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过双减和清算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地改革一两年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全村人口三百户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穷人的地位都改变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄模范出多少，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一件小事对您谈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村西南角穷人多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"住着佃户张庆安，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出力流汗三十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃不饱来穿不暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的儿子叫张锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随母讨饭受饥寒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长到十岁去放牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三四岁学种田。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地改革翻身后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的思想有转变，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五六岁上当民兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争地主他当先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的身子长的壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手粗脚大膀子宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛铁投在火里炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他受痛苦和熬煎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地改革分了九亩地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分到堂屋三大间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道好似风雪路人赶回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得到欢喜和温暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青农民劳动好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他的日子过的欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二婶给他提亲家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闺女生在胡家庄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"佃户出身爱勤俭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"父亲名叫胡庭元，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闺女人材长的俊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"织布下地勤生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一天黄昏吃过饭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星刚出全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁娘正在院中坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起重要事一端，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这事就该早准备，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙把儿子来呼唤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁听到娘来喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一步走到娘跟前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘说：“咱们从前受饥饿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抱着棍子要饭餐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可怜你爹死的早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看不到这些新事面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱的收成还不错，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了吃穿有零钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我打算给你娶媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晚你也有陪伴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘老手脚不灵便，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼花不能做针线。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁低头不答话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他心里有数暗盘算——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“虽说如今婚姻不买卖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"添人进口总花钱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不如把钱先买牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买牛种地好生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"借人牲口要换工，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁地拉车真叫难。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小张锁抬头说了话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿把心事对娘言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱的家里才翻身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好象小树根不全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁不愿娶个好媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"免得再当光棍汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是生产更当紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买牛不能再迟延，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女家今年才十七，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再等一年不算晚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱家祖辈没有牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给人种地白流汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺爹一生受穷苦："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都只为地主压迫咱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主杀人不见血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还不清租粮和利钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶上荒年上大水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺爹饿死大路边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要长大树先生根，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子打算要长远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买牛种地发了家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再娶媳妇把家安。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起受苦好心酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘儿两个泪不干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦罢眼泪来说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“听儿说罢娘心安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年利津去逃荒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北风大雪腊月天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爹推着行李车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肚里饥饿身上寒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走一步来跌一步，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有烟火怎取暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶到半夜人栽倒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你爹死在大路边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我到村里求地主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主赶我门外边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主说：‘你家冻死是命短。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"别到俺这里打麻烦！’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀里抱你守尸骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哭了一夜又一天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卖了小车买席片，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把他埋在黄土山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起地主罪恶大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十天半月说不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今刚刚翻了身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有根底难周转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要想发家来致富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"先买牲口买锄镰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过个一年零半载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"衣服床柜都买全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那时给你娶媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里外头都体面。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁买牛娘同意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶集卖米去换钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘纺花织布卖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抽空还把草帽编。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年底赚了十几万，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买个小牛手里牵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牵着小牛回家转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁心里多喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路之上唱小曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱个发家大生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从前放牛为地主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一年四季受饥寒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天买牛为自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨面种地不作难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边想来一边唱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不远来到家门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙把亲娘来叫喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“看这小牛沾不沾？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘正在纺棉线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"急忙迎到门外边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸住小牛尾巴骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就把小牛夸一番："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“小牛生的猛虎样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个小牙才出全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尖尖角来黑蹄子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全身皮毛黄闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四条小腿象木柱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能载重量腰不弯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨面犁地有力气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩平身长屁股圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好好好来真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个小牛我喜欢。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁忙的更有劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴里不说心喜欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬过米来打谷草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收拾牛槽把它拴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁喂牛且不表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再说西邻黄大川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他爹也是老佃户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从小受苦受艰难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十六岁上去参军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当过连部通讯员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十九岁上当战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀敌冲锋他当先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大战杨湖挂了彩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荣退回村再生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加土地改革斗地主，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导群众把身翻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分子一只老黄牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十亩好地屋九间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娶个媳妇身手好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养猪喂牛勤纺棉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他一年四季爱劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做事公正人不偏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众开会来选举，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选他担任工作员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一天正在屋里坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁找他来商谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俩人从小在一起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光着屁股满街玩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰到一起好亲热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不啦闲呱谈生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他见张锁走进门，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙把椅子给他搬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁坐在椅子上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把买牛说一番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说：“你的小牛买的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以后种地有靠山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我虽有牛身子软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里重活没学全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上级提倡搞互助，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多合伙好生产。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁听了他的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里喜欢忙答言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“找你正是为互助，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你不说来我要谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我家有个小黄牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加上你的大老牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两个牲口都有力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕田拉车多方便，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地里轻活你去做，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出力重活我来担。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说：“互助合作为自家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人多生产好盘算，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再找大柱和王五，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四家合伙不费难。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俩人说罢订计划，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日子一转到春天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹的河水开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春风吹的土地软，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨柳树枝都发青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民耕地打响鞭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁套上小黄牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有大川的老牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四家合伙搞互助，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耕地下种搞生产。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁劳动加油干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不吃烟酒不花钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天背着粪箕子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打扫灰土忙不闲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养个小猪多积肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粪堆攒的象土山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一车一车撒下地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春耕为了盼秋天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一场春雨落平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小苗青青都出全，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁看了心欢喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"割草喂牛忙黑天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"圈里天天垫干土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛不生灾粪多多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人家饮牛用坑水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁饮牛井上担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"槽里多多加草料，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喂的小牛肥团团。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月里来小麦黄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁割麦到村前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川王五帮他收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手里拿着小镰刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一镰一把割的快，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一边割来一边谈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说：“你的麦子长的好”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁说：“都只为互助搞生产”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说：“从前拉车没有牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己收割自己担”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁说：“一个小牛拉不动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还得帮它拖车尾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等到上岗下坡路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出力拔筋象拉铅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在拉车真容易，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有了小牛和老牛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骨骨碌碌拉回家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再到场里用积粪。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王五说：“没牛生产搞不好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有牛生产多一半。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说说笑笑真快乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三天不到麦收完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夏天锄地肩并肩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁跟着黄大川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"细工除草苗子好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两遍三遍地锄草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高粱长到丈把高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谷子出穗黄鲜鲜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棒子地里带绿豆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红萝卜种在地头边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话不及秋天到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民欢喜象过年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川夫妇割谷子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁跑来助一番，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉汗衫齐下手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好比冲锋到阵前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐心互助收割罢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成垛的庄稼满场放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们粮食打的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩要合九斗三。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"村里检查互助组，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁大川是榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收罢秋来早犁地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再搞副业过冬天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"买来几捆柳条子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学编粪箕和筐篮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又是一天晚饭后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上的星星打闪闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮明月东方升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照到张锁的小当院。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南墙底下麦秸垛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杆秸堆的到屋旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小夹道里藏谷草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗户底下砌羊草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨树枝上挂辣椒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一串一串红艳艳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母子两人对面坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把心事细细谈："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘说：“看见今年收成好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今后日子不作难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互助种地收成好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰衣足食有吃穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想起从前受苦罪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做梦谁望有今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这都是共产党的办法好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导翻身搞生产，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿着今年比往年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天上地下不一般。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁一旁忙答言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“从今土地归自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱的日子过的欢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动出力有吃穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犁完秋地去打坯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再盖新屋两三间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把小牛抚养大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"车套锄犁都买全。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘喜的拍拍手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等儿说忙插言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“咱的日子向上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好似太阳到中天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"收罢秋来娶媳妇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安家立业干一番，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你到地里多劳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺和媳妇多纺棉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娘明年怀里抱个小孙孙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俺的老年不孤单。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母子两人正说话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门外来了黄大川，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉条板凳给他坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在凳上就吃烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说话慢吞吞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件消息要他传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“村里成立合作社，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"磨粉打油熬硝盐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了发家搞副业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大伙经营好赚钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们都该入股。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学点本领多生产。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"母子听罢他的话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮了精神壮了胆："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“这个办法就的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱得入股做社员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常言道‘一条线来容易断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千条线来拉不断’。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动出力靠自己，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合作生产大伙干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种罢田地搞副业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的光景大改变。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大川说：“咱的光景真好转，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要发家添人烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁快到二十岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就该娶亲成家眷。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁听了心里笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他娘听了喜洋洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忙到屋里点上灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉着大川听端详："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“娶亲之事准备好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做了被褥和衣衫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"做成一对花枕头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多亏大菊来帮忙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕子飞来一双双，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好女要配模范汉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁是个笨孩子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可巧找到一个俊姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快找你二婶子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"通知胡家做嫁妆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今晚说话算定亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月十五娶新娘。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说话不远日子到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张锁娶亲闹新房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四邻亲友来贺喜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓乐喧天喇叭响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小三喊大五，老李喊老王，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大菊叫小凤，二婶叫大娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你推我，我拉你，门里门外闹嚷嚷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说这个媳妇劳动好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今后，张锁的日子向上升，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他是翻身发家的好榜样。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四八年十月初稿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同年十二月改稿"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}